org.cip4.elk.alces.swingui.tree.message
Class AbstractMessageNode

java.lang.Object
  javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
      org.cip4.elk.alces.swingui.tree.message.AbstractMessageNode
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.tree.MutableTreeNode, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode, Message
Direct Known Subclasses:
InMessageNode, OutMessageNode
public abstract class AbstractMessageNode
extends javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
implements Message

A DefaultMutableTreeNode implementation of a Message. This class wraps a non-Swing implementation of a Message. The wrapped Message contains the logic, this class is simply a wrapper so that the Message can be displayed in a Swing JTree.

Version:
$Id$
Author:
Claes Buckwalter
